  ('social-worker-moex-07232', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-101-694fe135', 'sub-social-worker-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不屬於對「充權或增強權能（empower）」的描述？', '["個人無法實現自己的理由，主要是因外在環境的壓迫與限制", "鬆動壓迫環境的策略主要是依賴社工師（員）的倡導（advocacy）", "不論案主經歷多少無能或失利經驗，應視案主是有能力且有價值的個人", "藉由受壓迫的個人或團體的集體行動，促成壓迫環境的改善"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "639c6a9b062b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f322bd0dc24c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101030", "c": "902", "s": "0804", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作直接服務", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第一次專技醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師藥師醫事檢驗師護理師護士社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07233', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-101-694fe135', 'sub-social-worker-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '就生態系統觀點而言，個人在社區中所擁有的成員地位，係指下列何者？', '["人際關連（relatedness）", "棲息地（habitat）", "適配程度（goodness of fit）", "位置（niche）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "639c6a9b062b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f322bd0dc24c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101030", "c": "902", "s": "0804", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作直接服務", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第一次專技醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師藥師醫事檢驗師護理師護士社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
